    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chunky chips have been cooking for 15 min, heat a large wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a high heat</p><p>Once very hot, add the <strong>seasoned sirloin steak</strong> to the pan</p><p>For rare, cook for 2-3 min max on each side; for medium-rare, cook for 3-4 min on each side; for medium, cook for 4-5 min on each side</p><p>Once the steaks are cooked, transfer them to a plate to rest</p>",
